Name: assign_worker_to_team
Description: Binary variable indicating if a worker is assigned to a team

Name: select_feature_for_sprint
Description: Whether a feature is selected for current sprint

Name: plan_sprint_duration
Description: Planned duration of a sprint in days

Name: allocate_effort_per_task
Description: Assigned effort units to a task

Name: schedule_release_date
Description: Planned release date as numeric (days from epoch)

Name: estimate_story_points
Description: Estimated story points for a user story

Name: define_team_size
Description: Number of workers in a team

Name: choose_backlog_priority
Description: Priority level assigned to backlog item (1-5)

Name: moderate_retrospective_count
Description: Number of retrospectives moderated by Scrum Master

Name: set_influence_weight
Description: Weight assigned to stakeholder influence level

Name: plan_roadmap_timeline
Description: Time span of roadmap in days
